Small Package Delivery Service
NOR-CAL AIRLINES
HERE'S HOW IS WORKS
1.
Take your parcel to the Nor-Cal Passenger
ticket counter at the airport up to 30 minutes
before flight time.
2.
Nor-Cal's agent tags your parcel for the flight
request and
gives you a copy of the
Airbill covering your shipment.
3.
Simply phone your consignee at the destination
and give him
the flight number, Airbill number
4.
Your consignee then picks up the package at
his airport terminal. It will be at the regular
baggage claim counter within 30 minuter after
arrival.
The
maximum declared value
$50.00.
The
accepted is
general commodity charge
$5.25 per shipment (tax included) between any
two of the points shown below:
Chico - Nut Tree - Oroville - Red Bluff
Redding - Sacramento
San Francisco - Willows|
Package up to 50 Ibs. and not over 18" in any
dimension will go on the flight you specify.
NOR-CAL AIRLINES special handling for
small packages in a big hurry is made-to-order
for fast delivery of such items as:
Important Papers
Data Cards
Business Records
TV Film
Display Samples|
Fashions
Drugs & Serums
X-Rays
Tape Recordings
Small Parts
Engraving Plates
Blueprints
Phone Any
NOR-CAL AIRLINES
ticket office for flight information
CALL TOLL FREE
FROM ANYWHERE IN NORTHERN CALIFORNIA
